{"tid":1084760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港而家真係好奇怪，發生咩事","createTime":"2019-03-30T15:59:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T16:32:36.000Z","uid":194606,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dddb2a3408df1118417347fef7515e635c917f02","tid":1084760,"uid":194606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T15:59:54.000Z","msg":"[發洩文]<br />\n<br />\n仆街啦屌。。。<br />\n究竟呢個係唔係香港嚟㗎...<br />\n<br />\n最近我所熟悉嘅人講啲嘢我聽唔明更加唔想去明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜撚嘢出街去餐廳嗌嘢食，條友講「點菜」<br />\n<br />\n行街見到個花樽幾靚，佢講「花瓶」<br />\n<br />\n最common... 有嘢未登記嘅都講「開通」<br />\n<br />\n我係唔係返咗古代？<br />\n個個都講書面語嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好銀耳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n除此之外，我去開嘅百貨公司同埋我所住嘅地方，出到街附近嘅人好多都喺度講普通話，啲細路呀，大人呀，唔睇清楚我喺邊以為返咗大陸 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返到學校... 我啲同學日撚日都喺度睇咩抖陰，睇到冇哂電插住尿袋繼續睇，之後又追埋啲支那男團去睇演唱會... 出去買嘢畀錢就淨係識用支那寶、We7 Pay。電話打字用普通話拼音 <br />\n<br />\n返咗兩個sem啦，都好似同佢哋冇乜話題，分隔咗兩個世界咁，可唔可以教下我點樣搵共同話題？講明我係絕對拒絕大陸嘢嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n真係未到2047香港 Hong Kong 就已經變成Xiang Gang <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n還我香港 plz <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28beb7590a37539565796572c04374ab5cc1e7a9","tid":1084760,"uid":194606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:08:18.000Z","msg":"有冇得避免點樣可以唔好俾呢啲人同化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出到街又有返學又有就連喺屋企都有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98f416b68a7c6e0774f259f0058574e2d3b1d228","tid":1084760,"uid":118120,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:15:04.000Z","msg":"你見到d 本地小朋友都用普通話做母語就知咩事<br />\n到佢地大個, 你就會見到香港既工作場所變成用普通話多過廣東話<br />\n講廣東話隨時俾人歧視番轉頭"},{"pid":"65b0573c3991688a9600be5061c4f59f0d0639b0","tid":1084760,"uid":49392,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:17:57.000Z","msg":"去餐廳，成日聽人嗌寫嘢去表示點餐，究竟邊個諗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c1520ae29f3bea3dcacc0221c9734f99eb6438","tid":1084760,"uid":196099,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:19:11.000Z","msg":"去大牌檔嘅話應該全部都係「寫野」<br />\n因為支那人唔會去大排檔"},{"pid":"9d58d8ee0c6f4059ed830f8c0c68018c4de6685b","tid":1084760,"uid":33635,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:20:47.000Z","msg":"書咩嘢面語<br />\n而家啲支那用詞全部都俾人用「書面語」嚟做包裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最簡單 開通 -&gt; 啟動<br />\n<br />\n呢啲唔係都係書面語咩？"},{"pid":"d4db5c54e0b0299a1954c5b6ee71661cd759d889","tid":1084760,"uid":194606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9d58d8ee0c6f4059ed830f8c0c68018c4de6685b","tid":1084760,"uid":33635,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:20:47.000Z","msg":"書咩嘢面語<br />\n而家啲支那用詞全部都俾人用「書面語」嚟做包裝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最簡單 開通 -&gt; 啟動<br />\n<br />\n呢啲唔係都係書面語咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"唉屌 sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗我真係俾佢哋搞亂曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f33b15e28dd052c099b04b22b7e0aee14e4fa0c0","tid":1084760,"uid":143306,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"你自己on9接受唔到新事物"},{"pid":"2f46308c3b333b5bae799592bf9d6a1d466ea321","tid":1084760,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:26:58.000Z","msg":"連登都赤化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb2811043c709e8df81e6db7dc39ba71fdb2bf1","tid":1084760,"uid":29093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T16:28:07.000Z","msg":"書面語<img sr